  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/c0c21b80e49bc3e6c50b7c8a69776109.avif?t=1749034073\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/7a3066f4d687355224b8c40042c6b101.poster.avif?t=1749034073\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/7a3066f4d687355224b8c40042c6b101.webm?t=1749034073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/2066c6c1b7869282a2c529d7747bfb09.avif?t=1749034073\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a surprise betrayal from his most trusted mage, the king of Lescardia falls ill from the effect of the mage's curse, and a mysterious labyrinth formed out of darkness subsequently appears in the ruins outside of the city. A few days later, swarms of ferocious monsters begin to emerge from the labyrinth, and the people of Lescardia start to panic as the kingdom is thrown into chaos by the upheaval.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon Crawling RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quest System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-Depth Battle System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster Book</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots and lots of Loot!</p></li></ul></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/c0c21b80e49bc3e6c50b7c8a69776109.avif?t=1749034073\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/7a3066f4d687355224b8c40042c6b101.poster.avif?t=1749034073\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/7a3066f4d687355224b8c40042c6b101.webm?t=1749034073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211830/extras/2066c6c1b7869282a2c529d7747bfb09.avif?t=1749034073\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a surprise betrayal from his most trusted mage, the king of Lescardia falls ill from the effect of the mage's curse, and a mysterious labyrinth formed out of darkness subsequently appears in the ruins outside of the city. A few days later, swarms of ferocious monsters begin to emerge from the labyrinth, and the people of Lescardia start to panic as the kingdom is thrown into chaos by the upheaval.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon Crawling RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quest System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-Depth Battle System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster Book</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots and lots of Loot!</p></li></ul></p></li></ul>",
